      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting an exceptional specimen maintained to the highest standards of automotive preservation. This vehicle exhibits showroom-quality aesthetics and mechanical integrity, representing a rare opportunity for the discerning collector or enthusiast. Every surface and component reflects a history of meticulous care, ensuring a driving experience indistinguishable from its original production state. This is an investment-grade acquisition for those who demand nothing less than absolute excellence.",
