    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional vehicle that redefines the standard for 'pre-owned.' This car is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, factory luster thanks to a professional ceramic coating, showing absolutely no swirls, chips, or imperfections even under direct light. Inside, the cabin remains pristine; the premium leather seats show zero bolster wear, and the original floor mats look untouched. Mechanically, it is indistinguishable from new, with a comprehensive service history performed exclusively by certified technicians. Every button, sensor, and electronic feature functions exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a collector-grade example intended for the discerning driver who settles for nothing less than perfection. It comes with all original keys, manuals, and a clean title in hand.",
      "price": 46500.0,
