    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! Are you looking for a ride that feels like it just rolled off the lot? I\u2019m parting with my absolute pride and joy, and let me tell you\u2014it is in pristine condition! I\u2019ve taken such good care of this beauty; it\u2019s basically spotless inside and out and drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, and that 'new car' feel is still very much alive. I\u2019m so excited for the next owner to enjoy it as much as I have. Come take a look and see for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
