    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a superlative E46 M3 in collector-grade condition. This example features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333hp through individual throttle bodies to a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox. The mechanical integrity is absolute: the Vanos system has been fully overhauled, and the rod bearings have been replaced as preventative maintenance. The rear subframe\u2014a known point of failure\u2014has been professionally reinforced. The chassis retains its factory-spec torsional rigidity with refreshed bushings and a flawlessly functioning M Variable Differential Lock. Finished in original paint with an interior devoid of typical bolster wear, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of naturally aspirated BMW performance. Comprehensive service history and Blackstone oil analysis included.",
